.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Represents an enemy character controlled by a finite state machine (FSM)\&. This class defines properties, behavior, and state transitions for an enemy AI agent\&. It is integrated with ECS (Entity-Component System), physics, animation, and health systems\&. 
